channel.description:

item.title: Hey Can Someone Help Me With This?
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

[quote=“gunz4life, post:2, topic:291364”] @echo off javac *java pause >nul
its that or

@echo off
java *javac
pause >nul

Both of them confuse me, haha:P[/quote]

You don’t need the >nul or @echo off, and it’s javac as o.O O.o pointed out.
